data.description: Under construction now, our 'Rio Grande' floorplan is expected to be completed by this November 2022! Our Monzano Vista community has large lots and sits up high above the valley with beautiful views of Tome Hill. Home will have plenty of light with lots of windows, recessed lighting and 9 feet ceilings. The kitchen features dark brown cabinets with formika coutertops and large 12X12 ceramic tile in all wet areas. An island that looks out over the family room. Lots of storage with big pantry and utility room. Master bedroom located on main level has great separation from the other 4 bedrooms PLUS large loft located upstairs. Stay cool with the refrigerated air and low e vinyl windows. Plus, when you use our in house lender, you'll receive 5000K towards closing costs.
